comments.content: Plus [Edwardian Script Alt](http://web.archive.org/web/20150417101747/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/itc/edwardian-script/edwardian-scr-alt/) (Schlemmer-Oase) and probably [VAG Rounded](http://web.archive.org/web/20150417101747/http:/www.identifont.com/show?26D) for »süß & salzig«.
